{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839038464,"sessionID":"ses_287c1a8faffeeokE1uwfD9WZT1","part":{"id":"prt_d783f79bb001JEGdwps03rmoTs","messageID":"msg_d783f3851001vqS1Db1Qo9mPP2","sessionID":"ses_287c1a8faffeeokE1uwfD9WZT1","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","content":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine the `AgentRuntime` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agent workloads. This work establishes the core API surface — `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and supporting shared types — that the Workload Manager controller and generated `client-go` library consume.\n\n## Scope\n\n### In scope\n\n| Item | Detail |\n|------|--------|\n| **Package** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\n| **API group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| **Version** | `v1alpha1` |\n| **Types defined** | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\n| **Scheme registration** | `groupversion_info.go`, `register.go` — `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`, kind constants, `Resource()` helper |\n| **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn`, validation/default markers |\n| **Code generation** | `controller-gen crd` → `manifests/charts/base/crds/`; `controller-gen object` → `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`; `k8s.io/code-generator` → `client-go/` |\n| **Generated client surface** | `AgentRuntimeInterface` (Create/Update/UpdateStatus/Delete/DeleteCollection/Get/List/Watch/Patch), `AgentRuntimeInformer`, `AgentRuntimeLister` |\n\n### Out of scope\n\n- `CodeInterpreter` CRD types (separate AR)\n- Workload Manager HTTP API routes and handlers\n- Reconciler/controller logic\n- Helm chart CRD YAML rendering (consumes output, not produced here)\n- RBAC / ServiceAccount definitions\n\n## Design\n\n### File layout\n\n| File | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` | `+groupName` marker, `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme` |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Kind constants (`AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeListKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`), `SchemeGroupVersion`, `Resource()` helper |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus` |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Auto-generated by `controller-gen object` |\n\n### Type definitions\n\n**`AgentRuntime`** — namespaced CRD with `status` subresource:\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**`AgentRuntimeSpec`** — sandbox template and session constraints:\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n}\n```\n\n**`AgentRuntimeStatus`** — condition-based status:\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**`AgentRuntimeList`**:\n\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n**Shared types** (`TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate`):\n\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    // +optional\n    PathPrefix *string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Name *string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n    Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    // +optional\n    Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\"`\n}\n```\n\n### Scheme registration\n\n**`groupversion_info.go`**:\n\n```go\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n\nvar (\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n    AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n**`register.go`**:\n\n```go\nvar (\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n### Code generation pipeline\n\n```\ncontroller-gen crd  → manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\ncontroller-gen object → pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go\nk8s.io/code-generator → client-go/ (clientset, informers, listers, fakes)\n```\n\nInvocation: `make gen-all` → `generate` (controller-gen) + `gen-client` (`hack/update-codegen.sh`).\n\n## Impact analysis\n\n### Files created\n\n| File | Lines (est.) |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` | ~25 |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | ~25 |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` | ~60 |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | ~45 |\n\n### Files generated (not hand-edited)\n\n| File | Tool |\n|------|------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | `controller-gen object` |\n| `manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml` | `controller-gen crd` |\n| `client-go/` (entire tree) | `k8s.io/code-generator` |\n\n### Downstream consumers\n\n| Consumer | Dependency |\n|----------|-----------|\n| `client-go` typed client | Imports `runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime` / `AgentRuntimeList` for CRUD operations |\n| `client-go` informers/listers | Uses `AgentRuntimeInformer`, `AgentRuntimeLister` built from these types |\n| Workload Manager controller | Imports types for sandbox lifecycle reconciliation |\n| Helm chart CRDs | Rendered YAML consumed by `kubectl apply` / Helm install |\n| Fake clients | `client-go/.../fake/` test doubles for unit testing |\n\n### Breaking change risk\n\n- **Low**: This is a greenfield type definition. No existing runtime behavior is modified.\n- **Future**: Adding required fields to `AgentRuntimeSpec` after initial release will require CRD version bump (`v1alpha1` → `v1alpha2`) and conversion webhook.\n\n## Alternatives considered\n\n### 1. Standalone CRD YAML (no Go types)\n\n**Approach**: Write CRD manifests directly as YAML without Go type definitions.\n\n**Rejected because**: AgentCube uses Go controllers (Workload Manager) that require typed Go structs for serialization, validation, and scheme registration. YAML-only CRDs would force manual JSON unmarshaling and lose compile-time type safety.\n\n### 2. Kubebuilder/controller-runtime scaffolding\n\n**Approach**: Use `kubebuilder create api` to scaffold the full controller + CRD project structure.\n\n**Rejected because**: AgentCube's Workload Manager is a Gin-based HTTP service, not a controller-runtime manager. The project uses `controller-gen` for type/code generation only, without the controller-runtime manager scaffolding. Adopting Kubebuilder would introduce an unnecessary runtime dependency and project structure mismatch.\n\n### 3. Multi-version API from day one (`v1alpha1` + `v1beta1`)\n\n**Approach**: Define two API versions simultaneously with a conversion webhook.\n\n**Rejected because**: The project is pre-GA with no existing users. A single `v1alpha1` version is sufficient for initial development. Adding versions and conversion webhooks adds operational complexity without current benefit.\n\n### 4. Embed full `corev1.PodTemplateSpec` instead of custom `SandboxTemplate`\n\n**Approach**: Use `corev1.PodTemplateSpec` directly in `AgentRuntimeSpec` rather than the lighter `SandboxTemplate` wrapper.\n\n**Rejected because**: `SandboxTemplate` provides a controlled surface — optional `labels`/`annotations` maps with a required embedded `corev1.PodSpec` — while keeping the CRD schema focused on what AgentCube manages. Full `PodTemplateSpec` would expose `ObjectMeta` fields that are not relevant to sandbox template configuration.\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | `v0.34.1` | `metav1.TypeMeta`, `metav1.ObjectMeta`, `metav1.Duration`, `metav1.Condition`, `schema.GroupVersion` |\n| `k8s.io/api` | `v0.34.1` | `corev1.PodSpec` embedded in `SandboxTemplate` |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | `v0.22.2` | `scheme.Builder` for scheme registration |\n| `controller-gen` | `v0.17.2` | CRD YAML and deepcopy generation |\n| `k8s.io/code-generator` | `v0.34.1` | client-go library generation |\n\n## Verification\n\n```bash\n# Generate CRD YAML, deepcopy, and client-go\nmake gen-all\n\n# Verify no diff (all generated files committed)\nmake gen-check\n\n# Validate CRD schema\nkubectl apply -f manifests/charts/base/crds/ --dry-run=server\n```\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775839038448,"end":1775839038461}}}}
